message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Digital Rendering Engineering: The Physics of Light - Companion Code"
authors:
  - family-names: "Sage"
    given-names: "JM"
    affiliation: "Optics Optimization Laboratory"
repository-code: "https://github.com/OpticsOptimizationLab/dre-physics-of-light"
