abstract: >-
  Production-quality HLSL implementations of physically-based rendering
  algorithms with automated energy conservation validation. Includes
  Cook-Torrance microfacet BRDF, VNDF importance sampling, Russian Roulette
  path termination, and comprehensive White Furnace testing.
